    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到<i>AutoBlobber</i>，这里将考验你的终极策略能力！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<i>AutoBlobber</i>中，策略决定一切。你无需直接控制移动或战斗，而是在每波敌人之间通过选择和放置升级项来引导你的角色。构建强大的协同效果，解锁强化能力，将你的角色进化成不可阻挡的存在——然后坐观混乱的战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>尽可能生存更久，冲击全球排行榜。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在波次间装备升级项</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/bd9a187fba02af323bdac8fa68798711.poster.avif?t=1772183306\" width=608 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/bd9a187fba02af323bdac8fa68798711.webm?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/bd9a187fba02af323bdac8fa68798711.mp4?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>拥有不同能力和目标模式的独特升级项</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/5e3435881d7853237486357f52111cfd.poster.avif?t=1772183306\" width=608 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/5e3435881d7853237486357f52111cfd.webm?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/5e3435881d7853237486357f52111cfd.mp4?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>迎战无数敌人，每波难度逐渐提升</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>组合升级项为更强版本</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/592082766e01a68568ba79162ac17d38.poster.avif?t=1772183306\" width=608 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/592082766e01a68568ba79162ac17d38.webm?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/592082766e01a68568ba79162ac17d38.mp4?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将基础升级项进化为更强版本，每种升级项有3个不同阶级</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >首领战！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/1adb226e966acf6468e368ac147dbefd.poster.avif?t=1772183306\" width=608 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/1adb226e966acf6468e368ac147dbefd.webm?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/1adb226e966acf6468e368ac147dbefd.mp4?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看看你的角色如何应对首领挑战！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用强化型升级项提升现有能力</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/76fa3884bc43fc7c6e61f60c9ec8e9de.poster.avif?t=1772183306\" width=608 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/76fa3884bc43fc7c6e61f60c9ec8e9de.webm?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/76fa3884bc43fc7c6e61f60c9ec8e9de.mp4?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用<i>&quot;强化型升级项&quot;</i>提升所有已装备升级项的属性</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>壮大你的&quot;角色军团&quot;，挑战生存极限</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/6d7bdb5df891a23637011d532ea12486.poster.avif?t=1772183306\" width=608 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/6d7bdb5df891a23637011d532ea12486.webm?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240250/extras/6d7bdb5df891a23637011d532ea12486.mp4?t=1772183306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >持续战斗、成长、购买新升级项，看看你能坚持多少波敌人。<br><br><i><u>全球</u>排行榜将展示谁是最强<strong>AutoBlobber玩家</strong></i>。<br><br><strong>你能登顶榜首吗？</strong></p>",
